room_title: Escape room "Elf Escape" by Mastermind Room Escape in St. Louis
room_description:
Uh oh! Your favorite elf just found out that his Dad made it on Santa's naughty list this year - and, what's worse, by stealing children's books! You've managed to find where the list is kept. You have to help the elf find new books for the kids and make Christmas Spirit grow in his dad's heart!
This escape room is also available at the St. Charles location: 3900 Old Hwy 94 S #1, St Charles, MO 63304. The contact phone number is 636-373-7801.
